label: After the Great Earthquake, 9:54 pm, August 31, 1886:  Earthquake Views, Charleston, S.C.
description: Souvenir booklet containing photographs of the aftermath of the Charleston Earthquake of 1886, featuring the damage done to buildings.  Published by Walker, Evans & Cogswell (Charleston, S.C.), 1886.  Photographs by Heliotype Printing Co., Boston, Mass.  [24] leaves of plates, 12 x 20 cm.
